"count":1},{"word":"save","count":1},{"word":"reminiscing","count":1},{"word":"later","count":1},{"word":"hurt","count":1},{"word":"stabilized","count":1},{"word":"doctor","count":1},{"word":"watch","count":1},{"word":"proceed","count":1},{"word":"alone","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"retrieval","count":1},{"word":"impression","count":1},{"word":"wrong","count":1},{"word":"seem","count":1},{"word":"lighter","count":1},{"word":"hopeful","count":1},{"word":"happier","count":1},{"word":"bad","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"contaminated","count":1},{"word":"including","count":1},{"word":"perspective","count":1},{"word":"healing","count":1},{"word":"left","count":1},{"word":"man","count":1},{"word":"become","count":1},{"word":"release","count":1},{"word":"sleeps","count":1},{"word":"local","count":1},{"word":"unstable","count":1},{"word":"fluctuating","count":1},{"word":"levels","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"taking","count":1},{"word":"opportunity","count":1},{"word":"grant","count":1},{"word":"access","count":1},{"word":"hm","count":1},{"word":"unlocked","count":1},{"word":"move","count":1},{"word":"area","count":1},{"word":"stronger","count":1},{"word":"signal","count":1},{"word":"deployed","count":1},{"word":"developed","count":1},{"word":"frostland","count":1},{"word":"expeditions","count":1},{"word":"lets","count":1},{"word":"interact","count":1},{"word":"disrupted","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"try","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"All good on your end, golden boy? Lucilla mentioned the Exostrider in the frostlands just moved. Please tell me that was you?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"...You found her?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"Understood. But I do have to ask, on Lucilla's behalf: what's the status of the Core?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"That explains it. The Research Institute is reporting a spike in Voidmatter concentrations over Lahai-Roi. Void Storm activity is kicking up again...","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"Back when the Reactor Drive was in the sky, its annual self-diagnostics caused the Exostrider's Greatsword pointed at the Threnodian to weaken.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"The Exostrider is probably running the same procedure now to integrate what you returned. Best for you both to stay within the Academy until peak season passes.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"Next time you're in the infirmary, we should revisit your old plan. The one tied to the Exostrider, the Stridergate, and the Threnodian.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"For now… just be with Aemeath. It must be a great relief to have her back. I'm happy for you.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"You've earned a break, {PlayerName}. Get some rest.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":114000031},{"text":"Three days ago, when Helios was launched, we registered an unexpected spike in Voidmatter concentrations near Hyvatia. It interfered with the launch.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"We're still unsure what triggered the surge. But after comparing the waveforms with the device Professor Mornye brought back, we suspect it was an artificially induced Void Storm.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"And we found you unconscious close by.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"(Chuckles) You can relax. Professor Lucilla has already given you the clear. You're not a suspect.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"I'm just here for protective oversight. Acting as your personal bodyguard, you might say.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"Heh, a doctor's duty, isn't it? But there is one thing I need your testimony on.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"Before you fainted, who did you see?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000003},{"text":"************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"**********************************************************************************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"**************************************************************************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"****************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"***************************************************************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"***************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"****************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"***************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"***********************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"****************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"*********************************************************************************