"quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"****************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"**********************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"**********************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"*******************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"********************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"**************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"*******************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"*********************************************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"*********************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"What a coincidence to run into you here, {PlayerName}. This is a pleasant surprise.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"You came to the frostlands for the Exostrider?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"I'm headed the same way. I've got to check in on some researchers stationed out here on long-term fieldwork.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Having a guide might make the trip a little easier. What do you say?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Let me help you modify your bike. There are quite a few waterways, and its current setup might not handle them well.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"You pick up a few things when you come here as often as I do.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Look at this place, {PlayerName}. Hard to believe it, but years ago, all of this was a lush, green forest.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Back then, the Roya were nomads, the true natives of Lahai-Roi, who walked in step with nature itself.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Yes. It triggered a magnetic pole shift. From then on, Lahai-Roi became the new pole.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"But the Lament wasn't the only cataclysm stirring back then.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"In the past, we had already reached the stars. But at some point… the <te href=750035>Etheric Sea</te> spread to cover all of Solaris.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"From that moment on...","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Countless spacecraft were lost. Our space exploration programs were abandoned. And space became out of reach.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"But times have changed. Since its founding, the goal of Startorch Academy has been to use the Exostrider to explore space—whether through the Etheric Sea or the <te href=750036>Stridergate</te>.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"You know Lahai-Roi's history. Both the Exostrider and the Threnodian first came to Solaris through the Stridergate.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"The Academy has its theories, but here are two you might find interesting: <color=YellowD>the Stridergate is a gateway to outer space, and Aleph-1 is a Threnodian alien to Solaris</color>.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"With a gateway like that, of course we want to open it. But to pass through, we must awaken the Exostrider and be prepared to face Aleph-1 head-on.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"I've long believed that, Aleph-1 poses a far greater threat beyond Void Storms and Voidworms。","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"With other Threnodians, we can at least glean clues of their nature from their places of origin and the civilizations they emerge from. But Aleph-1… our knowledge remains blank.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"So many dream of being the voyager who returns from the stars, the first to walk the cosmos once more. But in all these years, no one has succeeded.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"The <color=RedD>Etheric Sea Phenomenon</color>… cast us into isolation. But it also gave birth to all our dreams of what could lie beyond.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"And those dreams… are still alive today.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Just my routine checks on the field researchers. {PlayerName} here has their own business to attend to, but we're headed the same way.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"What about you, Ms. Nivora? Chasing more fallen debris?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Run!","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Scaling that ice wall… It's too high, too risky. I'd rather not have a student on that climb.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"I've contacted the Academy. They're sending a rescue team. Once Nivora's safely returned, we'll set out again.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"With {PlayerName} on the team, a quick recon should be manageable. Up to you.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"I'd recommend you keep this private. Don't leave the recording for the Academy's teams to find.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Remember what I said earlier? It's a nest of competing factions. Anything connected to your past needs to be handled with discretion.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"So, what do you think? Leader... of the Black Shores.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Mm... friends, I'd say. Not the kind who lived in each other's pockets, but... as a Huanglong saying puts it, \"True friendships are still waters that run deep.\"","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"We met by chance, and by another twist of fate, you entrusted me with a rather long-term assignment.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"How about this: \"Strangers in passing who became confidants.\" How does that definition suit you?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"That's fine. Your work in Lahai-Roi won't be finished so soon, and we still have plenty of opportunities to reacquaint ourselves.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Heh, sorry, but it's the truth. We didn't spend much time together, but we got along instinctively.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Startorch is a web of competing interests. If this video leaks, it'd create quite the cleanup operation.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"After your sudden exit years ago, people were lining up to unpack your history. Solaris's golden boy, forever a mystery.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Heh... You're not the same as when we first met. But let's save the reminiscing for later.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Nivora's hurt. I've stabilized her, but as a doctor, I must stay to watch over her.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"From this point, you'll have to proceed alone. We'll wait here for the Academy's retrieval team.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Just my impression, I could be wrong. But you seem... lighter now.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"More hopeful. Happier.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"And that's... not a bad thing, {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Everything here has already been contaminated, including... it.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"From a doctor's perspective, the only healing left for what this man has become... is release.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"The Exostrider sleeps in these frostlands. Void Storm activity can make local frequencies unstable with <te href=750037>fluctuating Voidmatter levels</te>.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Oh, taking this opportunity, {PlayerName}, let me grant you access to the <te href=750038>Module Adapter</te>… Hm? It's already unlocked.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Let's move to an area with a stronger signal so it can be deployed.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"This Module Adapter was developed by Startorch Academy for frostland expeditions. It lets you interact with frequencies disrupted by Voidmatter.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Give it a try. You'll need it here.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001}]}